      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate correct implementation of governing equations through at least one analytical or manufactured solution benchmark.",
      "rationale": "Code verification was performed using the method of manufactured solutions for the incompressible Navier-Stokes equations. Observed convergence rates matched theoretical second-order spatial accuracy, confirming correct implementation."
