      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) for wall shear stress and velocity must be below 5% on the fine mesh.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study (coarse: 2.1M, medium: 5.8M, fine: 14.3M cells) yielded GCI values of 3.2% for velocity and 4.1% for wall shear stress on the fine mesh. Richardson extrapolation confirmed asymptotic convergence. Exceeds MRL 2 requirement."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
