    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 requirements for a Class II device with medium model influence. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions. The relative hemolysis index predictions agree with FDA benchmark experimental data within the 20% acceptance criterion across all five operating points. The assessment concludes that the model is fit for the stated COU.",
